# Ways to select categorical features
features_to_encode = list(X_train.select_dtypes(include = ['object']).columns) 
# Or alternatively, 
features_to_encode = X_train.columns[X_train.dtypes==object].tolist()

A good post for handling the categorical features
https://medium.com/analytics-vidhya/handle-missing-values-in-categorical-features-b7c5b073dda2
